<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27038484">「齐天大圣」用英文怎么翻译？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2998319" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">今天上课看到《西游记》译本中将“齐天大圣”翻译成the Great Sage Equalling Heaven,我个人总是觉得太死板了，难免有尴尬感……没有原文威风凛凛的感觉。到底这个称号怎么翻译比较好嘞？</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

