<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="186">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-ding-zhi-14" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-ding-zhi-14" class="zg-link" title="熊鼎">熊鼎</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2998319" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">Skywalker Prime<br><br>1. 天上走 - 齐天<br>（取的是物理意义上形象的天，舍了“寿与天齐”抽象的天。）<br><br>2. walker - 行者<br><br>3. 平时武器藏起来，打架拿出来伸长<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/f1e8e4316449e4e2b3a00bce152c73bd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/f1e8e4316449e4e2b3a00bce152c73bd_b.jpg"><br><br>4. 可扩展，想表现“大”、“圣”可以加上the Great，the Holy等，也便于后面太白金星等人称呼。<br><br>5. 与 <a data-hash="5109f6623201494c5a819995c5f36afb" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/5109f6623201494c5a819995c5f36afb" class="member_mention" data-editable="true" data-title="@郭动天" data-tip="p$b$5109f6623201494c5a819995c5f36afb">@郭动天</a>讨论变形金刚的翻译时，他提起博派领袖的中文译名中都带有一个“天”字，比如擎天柱，御天敌，刁炸天等。<br><br>这样翻译的原因是，汽车人首脑的英文原名中都带有一个“Prime”，意为“至高的，究极的”，与“天”对应。前面讲Sky是舍了“天”的抽象含义，这里正好用Prime补全了，并且也涵盖了“大圣”的霸气。<br><br>6. <a data-hash="13c74cb1bcaebf72248c6c28e1652a4c" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/13c74cb1bcaebf72248c6c28e1652a4c" class="member_mention" data-editable="true" data-title="@黄俊鹏" data-tip="p$b$13c74cb1bcaebf72248c6c28e1652a4c">@黄俊鹏</a> 贡献了一个更加形神具备的：<br><br>Sunwalker


</div>

</div>
